<snippet tags="earth" name="grandmother7">
    <div class="absoluteAlign bothHalves gameBg" style="background-image: url('assets/earth_livingroom.gif'); background-size: cover"></div>
    <div class="absoluteAlign blackBg textPanel">
        <p>"There shall be weeping and gnashing of teeth. God will create a special planet, and when judgment comes and they are carried away by the angels, bound hand and foot and cast into outer darkness, they're cast into this planet. And God will fling it into an outer cosmos and all through eternity it will drift further and further away from the light."</p>

        <p>[[⮕ Next|grandmother8]]</p>
    </div>
</snippet>

